Death Report Performance Analysis

Performance Analysis

Quick links to WarcraftLogs analysis tools for each pull

📋 What to look for:

Damage Taken: Identify who's taking avoidable damage from mechanics

Consumables: Verify everyone has proper flasks, pre-potted, and used healthstones

Defensive CDs: Check if players are using personals during high damage phases

Interrupts/Dispels: Ensure team coordination on priority mechanics
